query:
SELECT q.id, q.subjectId, s.name as subject_name, SUBSTR(q.question, 1, 30) as question_preview
FROM questions q
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON q.subjectId = s.id
ORDER BY q.subjectId, q.id;
